CSS Code:
```css
.chat-modal {
  display: none; /* Hide the modal by default */
  position: fixed; /* Position the modal fixedly */
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); /* Black background */
  z-index: 999; /* Make the modal on top of everything */
}

.chat-modal-content {
  display: flex; /* Flexible container for messages */
  flex-direction: column; /* Messages will be displayed vertically */
  align-items: center; /* Center the messages vertically */
}

.messages {
  display: flex; /* Flexible container for messages */
  flex-direction: column; /* Messages will be displayed vertically */
  align-items: center; /* Center the messages vertically */
}

.message {
  flex: 1; /* Equal width and height for each message */
  margin: 10px; /* Add some space between messages */
}

.bot-message {
  background-color: #f2f2f2; /* Light gray background for bot messages */
}

.human-message {
  background-color: #ccc; /* Dark gray background for human messages */
}

.chat-modal-btn {
  position: absolute; /* Position the button to the top-right corner */
  top: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  background-color: #4CAF50; /* Blue button */
  color: white;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

